1
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:52,870
Today is a very important day in our lives as Sahaja yogis.

2
00:06:54,740 --> 00:06:57,930
This is the day when Sahasrara was opened out,

3
00:06:59,730 --> 00:07:04,910
which was really a very charismatic thing that happened.

4
00:07:07,710 --> 00:07:08,910
I never expected

5
00:07:09,930 --> 00:07:13,730
that in My lifetime I'll be able to work it out,

6
00:07:14,700 --> 00:07:15,870
but it has been,

7
00:07:16,710 --> 00:07:21,790
and so many of you have got your Sahasrara opened.

8
00:07:24,730 --> 00:07:27,740
Without that you could never have known

9
00:07:27,900 --> 00:07:29,850
what is the truth.

10
00:07:31,790 --> 00:07:35,730
You were all lost, as everybody is.

11
00:07:38,740 --> 00:07:40,700
First of all,

12
00:07:40,820 --> 00:07:46,710
Sahasrara is the only way we can perceive,

13
00:07:46,910 --> 00:07:51,930
understand and know the reality.

14
00:07:55,900 --> 00:07:57,910
You have come to know

15
00:07:59,700 --> 00:08:01,900
as to what is the reality,

16
00:08:04,740 --> 00:08:06,880
and you are enjoying that state

17
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:12,880
where you know what is the reality.

18
00:08:16,820 --> 00:08:22,740
It's a great blessing that Sahasrara was opened out

19
00:08:23,710 --> 00:08:26,800
and all of you got your realization.

20
00:08:27,850 --> 00:08:30,800
Otherwise all talks are just talks

21
00:08:31,710 --> 00:08:32,910
-- has no meaning,

22
00:08:33,730 --> 00:08:35,730
has no understanding;

23
00:08:35,820 --> 00:08:42,710
and that's why My first anxiety was to open Sahasrara.

24
00:08:42,870 --> 00:08:44,800
That worked out,

25
00:08:45,710 --> 00:08:46,910
worked out well,

26
00:08:47,740 --> 00:08:49,760
and all of you have got

27
00:08:49,900 --> 00:08:52,740
your Sahasrara opened.

28
00:08:52,850 --> 00:08:54,840
It's a remarkable thing.

29
00:08:55,730 --> 00:08:59,790
Nobody can believe that so many of you have got

30
00:09:00,710 --> 00:09:05,740
your Sahasrara open, but I can see now clearly

31
00:09:05,820 --> 00:09:07,930
the light on top of your heads.

32
00:09:09,930 --> 00:09:14,710
Whatever you have achieved is remarkable, no doubt.

33
00:09:15,700 --> 00:09:18,710
It is because of honest searching,

34
00:09:18,930 --> 00:09:20,850
honest searching,

35
00:09:21,790 --> 00:09:23,760
that you have got it.

36
00:09:23,930 --> 00:09:26,700
My doing is nothing,

37
00:09:26,810 --> 00:09:28,920
because you were just there

38
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:34,740
like a lamp and I just enlightened it, that's all.

39
00:09:35,730 --> 00:09:37,740
It's not such a big thing to do,

40
00:09:38,700 --> 00:09:42,850
as you people have achieved your state,

41
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:47,750
state of enlightenment,

42
00:09:47,830 --> 00:09:49,920
that you got it because

43
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:53,810
you were hankering after it,

44
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:55,910
working it out,

45
00:09:56,830 --> 00:09:58,770
and you did it.

46
00:09:58,870 --> 00:10:00,920
It's very creditable.

47
00:10:01,830 --> 00:10:03,860
Credit doesn't go to Me, I think,

48
00:10:03,910 --> 00:10:06,780
because I had a open Sahasrara,

49
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:09,920
but to achieve that in you people

50
00:10:10,780 --> 00:10:14,910
was so joy-giving for Me.

51
00:10:15,890 --> 00:10:18,780
Now you will understand,

52
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:22,840
because if Sahasrara is not open you can't talk people,

53
00:10:22,920 --> 00:10:25,730
you can't say anything to them

54
00:10:25,810 --> 00:10:27,890
-- it's just they don't understand.

55
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:33,940
With the Sahasrara open your understanding improves so much.

56
00:10:34,810 --> 00:10:37,810
That is what has happened with all of you,

57
00:10:37,940 --> 00:10:39,940
and I'm so very happy

58
00:10:40,780 --> 00:10:43,810
that it's so many people there are sitting here

59
00:10:43,920 --> 00:10:46,860
who have got their Sahasraras open.

60
00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:49,780
And there are many who have not come.

61
00:10:49,920 --> 00:10:54,920
So it's a big achievement for human beings

62
00:10:55,890 --> 00:10:58,700
to get it so much collectively

63
00:10:59,730 --> 00:11:01,780
Sahasrara opened,

64
00:11:02,730 --> 00:11:06,780
by which you know the truth,

65
00:11:07,730 --> 00:11:09,720
absolute truth.

66
00:11:09,910 --> 00:11:13,730
Whatever you know after your realization

67
00:11:13,870 --> 00:11:15,840
is the absolute truth.

68
00:11:16,730 --> 00:11:17,940
You don't argue then,

69
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:19,920
don't question,

70
00:11:20,830 --> 00:11:24,760
you just know it and you accept it

71
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:26,800
as a knowledge.

72
00:11:26,880 --> 00:11:30,910
It's such a nice thing that it was all there,

73
00:11:31,730 --> 00:11:33,710
but it was not open.

74
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:37,940
And when it opened out, how people have understood Me

75
00:11:38,900 --> 00:11:41,830
and also the laws of the Divine.

76
00:11:42,790 --> 00:11:44,900
It's such a blessing of the Divine

77
00:11:45,820 --> 00:11:48,930
that you have got your Sahasrara opened out,

78
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:53,850
for which you may say, "We didn't do anything, Mother."

79
00:11:53,930 --> 00:11:55,800
It's not so.

80
00:11:55,940 --> 00:11:58,800
Your search for truth

81
00:11:58,880 --> 00:12:02,770
was intense and definite.

82
00:12:03,710 --> 00:12:05,800
You wanted to know the truth,

83
00:12:05,880 --> 00:12:07,880
that's why it has worked out.

84
00:12:08,740 --> 00:12:10,800
Otherwise no amount of money,

85
00:12:10,870 --> 00:12:12,740
no amount of effort,

86
00:12:12,770 --> 00:12:13,910
nothing would have helped.

87
00:12:14,850 --> 00:12:17,800
Sahasrara had to open by itself.

88
00:12:18,710 --> 00:12:22,850
It's all your building up, I should say,

89
00:12:23,710 --> 00:12:27,760
it's all your doing to yourself

90
00:12:27,830 --> 00:12:32,830
that has brought forth such a beautiful happening.

91
00:12:34,820 --> 00:12:40,910
I do not take any credit for that at all.

92
00:12:41,800 --> 00:12:44,900
Definitely I must say

93
00:12:45,800 --> 00:12:47,830
that I have made you understand

94
00:12:47,900 --> 00:12:52,770
that it's important that your Sahasrara should be opened.

95
00:12:52,880 --> 00:12:54,850
No more arguments,

96
00:12:54,940 --> 00:12:56,910
no more suggestions,

97
00:12:57,870 --> 00:13:01,830
nothing, but have your own Sahasrara open,

98
00:13:01,930 --> 00:13:04,850
which tells you what is the truth is.

99
00:13:05,850 --> 00:13:09,830
In these beautiful circumstances,

100
00:13:10,730 --> 00:13:12,820
what could your Mother say?

101
00:13:13,710 --> 00:13:19,730
I can only say that continue to live a life of reality,

102
00:13:19,770 --> 00:13:20,880
of understanding.

103
00:13:21,790 --> 00:13:23,840
In everything you will find

104
00:13:23,910 --> 00:13:25,790
there is truth,

105
00:13:25,900 --> 00:13:33,910
and how do we use that truth is our own achievement.

106
00:13:35,900 --> 00:13:40,710
People are lost

107
00:13:40,850 --> 00:13:43,760
because they have no knowledge.

108
00:13:43,910 --> 00:13:47,820
Knowledge from the books is no knowledge.

109
00:13:48,860 --> 00:13:50,900
Their knowledge must come from within,

110
00:13:51,700 --> 00:13:53,750
from within themselves, you see,

111
00:13:53,810 --> 00:13:57,870
and that has happened because of Sahasrara opening.

112
00:13:58,870 --> 00:14:01,810
In all the countries it has happened,

113
00:14:01,900 --> 00:14:04,810
and it will be in the whole world,

114
00:14:04,890 --> 00:14:07,860
so many people will get realization.

115
00:14:08,710 --> 00:14:12,900
But only thing I feel that you people should have

116
00:14:13,820 --> 00:14:17,870
no emotional attachment to it,

117
00:14:18,820 --> 00:14:22,940
not emotional but realistic attachment,

118
00:14:23,790 --> 00:14:28,760
that it is there, it has happened, it's working out.

119
00:14:28,850 --> 00:14:32,870
Then you will be able to give realizations to other,

120
00:14:33,710 --> 00:14:36,800
you'll understand the importance of realization.

121
00:14:37,710 --> 00:14:39,740
Unless and until you use it

122
00:14:39,820 --> 00:14:43,730
you won't know what is the power of realization is.

123
00:14:43,820 --> 00:14:47,790
So you must learn how to use this power

124
00:14:47,850 --> 00:14:48,930
which is within you,

125
00:14:49,740 --> 00:14:51,770
which has started working out,

126
00:14:51,850 --> 00:14:55,840
and which will give you such a immense capacity.

127
00:15:00,780 --> 00:15:04,840
My health is little bit gone down -- after all, I am very old.

128
00:15:04,920 --> 00:15:09,810
But still I don't feel tired in any way

129
00:15:10,700 --> 00:15:11,800
while addressing you;

130
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:14,730
I feel so enamored

131
00:15:14,830 --> 00:15:17,720
that there are so many Sahaja yogis,

132
00:15:17,760 --> 00:15:20,720
so many whose Sahasrara is opened,

133
00:15:20,760 --> 00:15:22,870
and they're enjoying their Sahasrara.

134
00:15:23,750 --> 00:15:26,780
Actually I would have liked you to ask Me questions,

135
00:15:26,900 --> 00:15:31,920
but you can write questions and send Me written ones.

136
00:15:32,750 --> 00:15:34,870
Then I'll try to answer them some time.

137
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:37,760
Will be a much better idea.

138
00:15:38,860 --> 00:15:40,840
So thank you very much.

139
00:15:40,920 --> 00:15:42,840
May God bless you.

140
00:15:43,750 --> 00:15:44,920
Grow into Sahaj,

141
00:15:45,900 --> 00:15:48,700
grow into your being.

142
00:15:48,800 --> 00:15:52,750
May God bless you, all My blessings.

